#FlySwiss #FlughafenZürich #PlaneSpotting #BlessUp

Great energy at the True Global Ventures 63rd Investor Luncheon.

Was great networking with some of the most visionary people in tech & venture capital. And listening to inspiring speeches from CEO‘s of Sandbox, Music Xray etc.

We‘re getting ready to launch @LuxoVision2030Fund, a $50 Million fund with my associates, to be deployed between 2024-2026. Focused on Web3 ventures in Entertainment, Sports, Aviation & Aerospace. Also utilizing the selected ventures to make an impact for people/communities in need, as with all my other business ventures :)

As our slogan says, „designing future, today“.

#LuxoVision2030Fund #LuxoGroupIntl #Vision2030 #VC #Fund #Future #Web3

Working on starting our first flagship @LuxoGroupIntl branded Luxo Hotels & Resorts in Maldives in 2024.

Happy Holidays Y’all!
Bless up!

#LuxoGroupIntl #LuxoResorts #Maldives

Ho Ho Ho 🎅🏾 
Have you been naughty or nice?

Regardless, I would like to wish you & your loved ones a Merryyy Christmas & Happy Holidays! 🎄🎄🎄 Ho Ho Ho 

Enjoy this season of joy with your loved ones🥂🥂

#BentleyRecords #WallStreet #RecordLabel

2022! What a year it’s been!! I’m excited for 2023, it’s gonna be an incredible year for all of us!

Here are some amazing evenings I enjoyed this year with my amazing friends ❤️

Grateful for all these moments, for every meal, every conversation! Looking forward to creating more memories next year! 🥂🥂

Bless up y’all! Y’all excited for the year ahead?

#PositiveVibesOnly

Happy New Years 2023 in advance to all my beautiful people worldwide! It’s gonna be an amazing year for everybody! God bless y’all! 🎆

I’m about to catch another red eye! The time I enjoy the most, and I get to relax & be creative is when I’m on air. Thanks to my „job“ I get to travel for work quite a bit. This past year I did a whoopin 61 flights. Didn’t help much with my obsession with airplanes lol. Here were some of my favorite cabins & flights I didn’t post much from lol.

1. & 2. Fly Dubai 737 Max 8
Great product for short/medium haul! Full lay flat. I was alone so the lovely air hostess indulged me with all the food & champagne available 🥹😆 Had a nice chat with the Captain real nice dude.

3. & 4. Swiss Airbus A330-300
Took me to the 70‘s with this very classy design & „The Throne“ seat was incredible! 😍 
Flight was only 40% full. So the Captain requested us not to switch seats for aircraft trim reasons.

5. Flying over the Swiss Alps. Unreal scenery.

6. & 7. Gulf Air Airbus A321LR
Amazing product! Most underrated airline imo. I was on an empty flight on one of those 🤯

8. Swiss Boeing 777-300ER

Great start to the year. Our team @LuxoGroupIntl is hard at work. We got some very exciting projects in the works for @LuxoAir, @Bentleyrecords.io, @BentleyRecords & @LuxoVison2030Fund. 
Relaunching @LuxoTravels as well. Got some crazy AI & Blockchain stuff in the works for @Bentleyrecords.io!
Big thanks to our board members and shareholders as always for their support.

Got some big humanitarian projects in the works for @LuxoHope that I’m super excited about as well!

Going extra hard this year 💯 Hope y’all having a great start to the year yourselves 🥂 Bless up my friends 🙏❤️ 

All praise to God!

#LuxoGroupIntl #Bentleyrecordsio #BentleyRecords #LuxoTravels #LuxoHope #GodFirst

social_posts.post_text:
March 2023. Hectic & Productive. Working 16 hours every fuckin day never felt nicer 💯
Exciting things in the works! Bless up! Happy Easter 🐣🐇 
Bahrain 🇧🇭 Istanbul 🇹🇷 London 🇬🇧 New York City 🇺🇸 Doha 🇶🇦 Dubai 🇦🇪

This statement here resonates very strong with me. I take immense enjoyment & pride in the work I do, matter of fact I’m fuckin obsessed with my work!
And how I utilize that “work” to assist as many people as humanly possible, in any way shape or form I can, to live their purpose. 

Ain’t about the money, fame or whatever superficial, just Grateful to the Big Man everyday for being able to live my purpose to the highest extent possible 🙏🏾

#BlessUp

May 24th 2023. Today is the first day of my second life. Yesterday was the day of resurrection, as it was all almost finito! 

Due to severe hypoxia caused by mixing up a medication(one of which is known to reduce insulin level) I take led to an adverse incident. And a few different things including a pressurized chest from a long flight, happening all at once, created the perfect storm inside my body. My heart almost stopped.

Big shoutout to our excellent first responders in New York City. Undoubtedly the best in the world. EMS came to me in less than 10 mins of my 911 call. These two Gentlemen on the photo practically saved my life!

And to the excellent doctors, nurses & staff @NypHospital who took excellent care of me.

Thank you God for letting me live to see another day 🙏🏾

I never take anything for granted either ways. But this moment made me realize you never know when is your last breath. So don’t forget to tell your people you love them today, don’t hold no petty bullshitass grudges with nobody & don’t take anything for granted. It could all be gone tomorrow!

I been going extra hard for the last 10 years, at 29 years and approaching 30 in a few months, maybe it’s a sign for me to slow down a little in the decade to come 😏

On the last picture here, you see the Gentlemen who made generous donations to build this amazing healthcare facility. And I made a pledge today to donate all my wealth at some point to healthcare through @LuxoHope Foundation.

Be safe! May God bless you all!

Love
LD

Back to work!
At @LuxoGroupIntl Global Headquarters. We have an exciting Quarter ahead! Some BIG news soon. Shareholders are gonna love it 😏

Last week was a tough one for me, had some time to reflect. But I’m back stronger than ever! 👊🏾

Big thanks to everyone who reached out. I truly appreciate each & every one of you who checked out on me, I mean it! I’m feeling so much better now, even better than before lol. To further improve my health & wellbeing I have decided to quit my occasional drinking, & smoking as well. It’s only gonna be good ole’ O2 from now on folks 🤠

Was overwhelmed by the messages, & quite emotional to see all the love 🥹 - calls, texts, DM’s, comments, emails, tweets etc. I will get back when I get a chance. 
Love y’all man ❤️
Bless up!
LD.

June 23’. Back stronger than ever. With a new found motivation. Let’s close these last 2 quarters of this year strong folks, let’s all win together 💪. Shoutout to everyone as always for the immense love & support! Got some exciting announcements soon..
P.S. Ain’t had a chance to check DM’s for a while, will do soon.. 
Bless up y’all ❤️

Love Y’all man. Bless up!
